00:16:27,919 --> 00:16:28,599
Putra Mahkota!

247
00:16:28,880 --> 00:16:29,280
Kau!

248
00:16:29,559 --> 00:16:30,080
Mundur!

249
00:16:30,280 --> 00:16:31,000
Jangan kemari.

