Kau masih datang membuatku
marah di saat seperti ini?

256
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:46,599
Aku hanya lakukan sesuai
instruksi Ayah.

257
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:48,380
Bukan sengaja membuat
Ayah marah.

258
00:16:49,239 --> 00:16:50,640
Dia…

259
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:51,679
Dia mau membuatku marah.

260
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:54,200
Dia berniat begitu, dia
sengaja melakukannya.

261
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:56,559
Apakah kau mau aku mati
di depanmu sekarang?

262
00:16:56,559 --> 00:16:57,719
- Putra Mahkota!
- Dasar kau.

263
00:16:58,559 --> 00:17:00,230
Kenapa kau juga mengacau
seperti ayahmu?

264
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:02,320
Kau sudah dewasa, masih saja
seperti anak-anak.

265
00:17:04,079 --> 00:17:06,200
Ayah, jika ada masalah,
turun dan katakanlah.

266
00:17:07,119 --> 00:17:07,680
Aku tidak mau.

267
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:09,119
Turun.

268
00:17:09,520 --> 00:17:10,359
Tidak!

269
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:13,400
Aku belum naik.

270
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:15,640
Bagaimana turun?

271
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:16,780
Putra Mahkota!

272
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:19,359
Satu.

273
00:17:21,280 --> 00:17:21,800
Dua.

274
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:24,400
Tiga.

275
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:28,280
Putra Mahkota!

276
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:30,040
Putra Mahkota!

277
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:31,380
Putra Mahkota!

278
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:33,640
Putra Mahkota, kau baik-baik saja, 'kan?

279
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:34,560
Selirku.

280
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:36,920
Kau mengagetkanku.

281
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:37,880
Sakit sekali.

282
00:17:38,359 --> 00:17:40,160
Ayah baik-baik saja, aku pulang dulu.

283
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:46,079
Selirku.

284
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,640
Putra Mahkota.

285
00:17:49,760 --> 00:17:51,330
Karena Putra Mahkota
baik-baik saja,…

286
00:17:51,640 --> 00:17:53,280
…aku juga pamit dulu.

287
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:55,730
Putra Mahkota istirahatlah
 lebih awal.

288
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:04,839
Putra Mahkota, kau mengagetkanku!

289
00:18:04,959 --> 00:18:05,719
Kau…

290
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:10,680
Kenapa kau menangis tanpa air mata?

291
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,439
Aku berteriak begini.

292
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:17,900
Apakah bisa terdengar sampai luar?

293
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:19,190
Menjawab Putra Mahkota.

294
00:18:19,439 --> 00:18:21,760
Gerakan sebesar ini,
pasti bisa terdengar.

295
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:25,599
Bantu aku berdiri.

296
00:18:33,319 --> 00:18:34,520
Aku ingin Kaisar…

297
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:37,040
Aku ingin Ayahanda mendengarnya.

298
00:18:37,800 --> 00:18:39,160
Aku tidak bersalah!

299
00:18:41,439 --> 00:18:42,270
Perintahkan mereka.

300
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:44,439
Segera siapkan makanan.

301
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:45,640
Aku sudah lapar.

302
00:18:46,560 --> 00:18:47,000
Baik.

303
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:50,680
Putra Mahkota, apa artinya ini?

304
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:53,079
Aku jadi bingung.

305
00:18:53,599 --> 00:18:54,920
Putra Mahkota.

306
00:18:57,599 --> 00:18:59,599
Pergi, cepat selidiki Selir Yu.

307
00:19:01,079 --> 00:19:01,599
Baik.

