00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:19,160
Yuan Qi.

309
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:24,160
Yuan Qi!

310
00:19:25,040 --> 00:19:25,599
Pangeran.

311
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:26,439
Pangeran.

312
00:19:27,920 --> 00:19:30,040
Hamba sudah menahannya, tapi gagal.

313
00:19:32,081 --> 00:19:32,425
(Yu)

314
00:19:38,560 --> 00:19:40,240
(Yu)

315
00:19:43,698 --> 00:19:46,900
(Divisi Masakan)

316
00:19:51,599 --> 00:19:53,280
Nanti robohkan saja pintunya.

317
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:56,920
Lagi pula, pintu tertutup
juga tidak ada gunanya.

318
00:19:57,680 --> 00:19:58,160
Baik.

319
00:19:59,520 --> 00:20:00,439
Tuan You.

320
00:20:00,760 --> 00:20:03,400
Apakah kali ini mencari pelayan
yang menyamar lagi?

321
