00:29:16,959 --> 00:29:19,319
Selir Yu jelas punya niat jahat.

436
00:29:21,479 --> 00:29:22,410
Mengidap penyakit apa?

437
00:29:23,439 --> 00:29:27,280
Bagaimana pelayan Biro Makanan
bisa mengetahui hal ini?

438
00:29:28,560 --> 00:29:29,160
Hamba…

439
00:29:31,079 --> 00:29:31,959
Hamba…

440
00:29:32,560 --> 00:29:33,280
Kenapa gemetar?

441
00:29:34,119 --> 00:29:35,439
Katakan dengan jelas!

442
00:29:35,560 --> 00:29:36,990
Ada Kaisar yang memberimu keadilan!

443
00:29:37,239 --> 00:29:38,439
Baik!

444
00:29:40,560 --> 00:29:42,920
Hamba berpikir belakangan ini…

445
00:29:45,359 --> 00:29:48,079
…daftar makanan Selir Yu
berubah drastis.

446
00:29:49,079 --> 00:29:52,040
Bahkan sering ada pelayan ambil
madu dan makanan manis.

447
00:29:52,479 --> 00:29:54,100
Orang di istana diam-diam
membahasnya.

448
00:29:54,880 --> 00:29:57,239
Mereka bilang Selir Yu sakit
dengan cara yang aneh.

449
00:29:58,880 --> 00:29:59,439
Kaisar.

450
00:30:00,359 --> 00:30:01,599
Hamba baru masuk istana.

451
00:30:02,119 --> 00:30:03,599
Bahkan tidak kenal jalan di istana.

452
00:30:04,599 --> 00:30:06,520
Tuan You bersikeras
menangkap hamba.

453
00:30:06,520 --> 00:30:07,820
Bertanya hamba punya niat apa.

454
00:30:08,119 --> 00:30:09,560
Hamba sungguh tidak tahu apa pun.

455
00:30:09,880 --> 00:30:11,839
Mohon ampun, Kaisar!

456
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:13,520
Ayahanda.

457
00:30:14,239 --> 00:30:16,079
Aku sungguh tidak bersalah.

458
00:30:21,599 --> 00:30:22,119
Kaisar.

459
00:30:22,760 --> 00:30:25,119
Saya minta izin panggil tabib
memeriksa Selir Yu di sini.

460
00:30:28,400 --> 00:30:31,599
Tabib Sheng dipersilakan masuk.

461
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:36,280
Untuk apa diperiksa?

462
00:30:37,520 --> 00:30:38,760
Biar kuberi tahu.

463
00:30:41,040 --> 00:30:45,599
Putra Mahkota mau bunuh Kaisar,
karena dia sudah bosan menunggu.

464
00:30:46,119 --> 00:30:48,719
Dia sudah tidak sabar
ingin jadi Kaisar.

465
00:30:51,439 --> 00:30:52,119
Aku…

466
00:30:54,079 --> 00:30:56,599
…diabaikan bertahun-tahun.

467
00:30:57,880 --> 00:31:01,119
Menerima seluruh perbuatan
buruk dan hinaan seluruh istana.

468
00:31:02,079 --> 00:31:04,000
Aku sudah bosan hidup dari awal.

469
00:31:04,280 --> 00:31:05,119
Selir Yu.

470
00:31:06,239 --> 00:31:09,359
Meski Kaisar jarang menemuimu,
tapi sangat baik padamu.

471
00:31:09,839 --> 00:31:11,719
