dendam sebesar ini?

472
00:31:12,439 --> 00:31:13,959
Kau malah begitu kejam.

473
00:31:14,359 --> 00:31:16,119
Kau mau menarik kami
mati bersamamu.

474
00:31:16,640 --> 00:31:17,599
Selir Zhuang.

475
00:31:18,479 --> 00:31:20,719
Kau kira Kaisar tulus
menyayangimu?

476
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:25,920
Kita hanyalah pajangan
keluarga kekaisaran.

477
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:27,520
Burung kepodang…

478
00:31:28,719 --> 00:31:31,319
…akan dilepaskan suatu hari nanti.

479
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:34,079
Namun, kita…

